<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Quản lý đoàn viên - Backend API</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Be+Vietnam+Pro:400,600&display=swap" />
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Be Vietnam Pro', sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7f6; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); text-align: center; max-width: 500px; }
        .logo { font-size: 50px; color: #3498db; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #333; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        p { color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .btn-portal { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #3498db; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; transition: background 0.3s; }
        .btn-portal:hover { background-color: #2980b9; color: white; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="logo">🚀</div>
        <h1>QuanLyDauTu API Backend</h1>
        <p>Hệ thống Backend (ASP.NET Web API) đang hoạt động bình thường trên cổng <strong>52369</strong>.</p>
        <p>Giao diện cũ (AngularJS) đã được gỡ bỏ. Vui lòng truy cập hệ thống qua giao diện Angular mới.</p>
        <a href="http://localhost:4200" class="btn-portal">Đi tới Frontend (localhost:4200)</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
